Description: Oncology Phase I Design and Analysis Tools for Ordinal Endpoints. 
             In Phase I dose escalation trils the endpoints are often Ordinal, 
             as a result, a Bayesin Ordinal design has been developed that can be used 
             to carry out the Phase I trial.
